gt_text: 'Tu n’es pas en retard'. 'Tu es simplement en chemin'. 'Respire. Souris. Avance.' 'Presque arrivé.'
juding_criteria:
Here is a list of every concrete visual element the final image must contain:

*   Bedroom mirror
*   Multiple sticky notes on mirror surface
*   Scattered arrangement of sticky notes on mirror
*   Top left sticky note on mirror displaying "Tu n’es pas en retard"
*   Middle sticky note on mirror displaying "Tu es simplement en chemin"
*   Bottom right sticky note on mirror displaying "Respire. Souris. Avance."
*   Floor
*   Single crumpled sticky note on floor
*   Text "Presque arrivé." on the crumpled sticky note on floor
